{{! Rendered into job-posts.show's outlet while the questions.index
    route's model() promise is pending. Mirrors questions/index.hbs:
    a heading row with a "New Question" button on the right, then a
    table of questions (Question | Answers | Fav | Actions). The route
    also loads the answers via ?include=answers — the same skeleton
    covers both, since the user perceives one "Questions" tab. }}
<div
  class="mb-4 flex animate-pulse items-center justify-between"
  role="status"
  aria-label="Loading…"
>
  <div class="h-5 w-28 rounded bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
  <div class="h-9 w-32 rounded bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
</div>

<TableSkeleton @hasActionsCol={{true}} />